<plot>This 2002 MTV Spring Break special aired to promote the soon to-be-released summer film Scooby-Doo. Freddie Prinze Jr., Sarah Michelle Gellar, Matthew Lillard, and Linda Cardellini send two teams of spring breakers on a clue-gathering journey through Cancun, Mexico that will ultimately lead them to the actors' secret location. There are 4 tasks to complete before they can find the actors and their secret location.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?092658</url></doc>
